<p>Feel free to take a closer look at <a href="https://bit.ly/35cobDU" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Avada&#8217;s</a> more recent release history here <a href="https://bit.ly/35cobDU" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">7.2</a>, <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/whats-new-in-7-1/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">7.1</a>, <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/whats-new-in-7-0/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">7.0</a>, <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/whats-new-in-6-2/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">6.2</a>, <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/whats-new-in-6-1/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">6.1</a>, <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/whats-new-in-6-0/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">6.0</a>, and beyond.</p>
<p>This article will be teasing some of the important new features coming to the Avada Website Builder 7.3 and some critically important changes. Let&#8217;s get started.</p>
