</div><div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-34 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><img width="1200" height="712" alt="Support Dashboard Welcome Image" title="Support Dashboard Welcome Image" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/dashboard-welcome-post.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-860408" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/dashboard-welcome-post-200x119.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/dashboard-welcome-post-400x237.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/dashboard-welcome-post-600x356.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/dashboard-welcome-post-800x475.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/dashboard-welcome-post.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px" /></span></div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-17 nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling" style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#eae9e9;border-style:solid;" ><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row"><div class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-20 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:50px;"><div class="fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-column-wrapper-legacy" style="background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;"><style type="text/css"></style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-83 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-left:0px;" id="ahead"><h2 class="title-heading-left" style="margin:0;">What Lies Ahead</h2></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-66"><p>Over time we have confirmed that the best way to develop and refine <a href="https://bit.ly/35cobDU" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Avada</a> is through community feedback and involvement. Head over to the <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/feature-voting/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">feature voting</a> page and place your vote now.</p>
<p>You can view the extensive Avada <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/installation-maintenance/avada-changelog/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">development changelog here</a>.</p>
