<p>The <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/avada-website-builder/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Avada Website Builder</a> has a vast array of features and styling options; however, you do not need to use all of them for your website, and this is where your style guide comes in. Decide upfront which styling options align with your brand and which design features are needed to make your website stand out.</p>
