<p>The Avada Website Builder has a vast array of Typography controls, options, and font selections to make your job easier. See this detailed <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/options/typography-options-in-avada/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">help file and video</a> to get you started.</p>
