e-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Title Element</a>, <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/text-block-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Text Box Element</a> and two <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/button-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Button Elements</a>, in the Right Column. </p>
