h: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-124"><p>This section uses a single Container with three 1/3 (33.33% width) Columns, each containing a <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/person-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Person Element</a>.</p>
<p>The Person Element allows you to add a personal profile, replete with image, name, title, description, and a whole bunch of styling options. </p>
