round-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;"><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-179{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-179{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-179 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-left:0px;" id="layouts"><h2 class="title-heading-left" style="margin:0;">Explaining Layouts &amp; Layout Sections</h2></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-142"><p>Before we look at the specific Layouts on the Avada Builder prebuilt website, the first thing to understand is the Layouts and Layout Sections&#8217; architecture. You can think of Layouts as a container for the page content. In contrast, the actual content comes from the various Layout Sections. There are four Layout Sections on a page â€“ the Header, Page Title Bar, Content, and Footer Layout Sections.</p>
<p>There is a default Global Layout, and any Layout Sections added to that will be shown on all pages of your website. There are Conditional Layouts with conditional logic to determine how the Layout will be used.</p>
<p>You can make as many Layouts and Layout Sections as you like, and you can use the Layout Sections in multiple Layouts. But you can only use a specific condition on a single Layout, so the theme knows which one to use.</p>
<p>See <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/fusion-builder/theme-builder/understanding-layouts-and-layout-sections/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Understanding Layouts &amp; Layout Sections</a> and <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/fusion-builder/theme-builder/understanding-conditional-layouts/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Understanding Conditional Layouts</a> for more info.</p>
</div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-68 hover-type-none"><img width="1989" height="1500" alt="Avada Layouts" title="Avada Layouts" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avadawebsitebuilder-layouts-example.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-840348" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avadawebsitebuilder-layouts-example-200x151.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avadawebsitebuilder-layouts-example-400x302.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avadawebsitebuilder-layouts-example-600x452.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avadawebsitebuilder-layouts-example-800x603.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avadawebsitebuilder-layouts-example-1200x905.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avadawebsitebuilder-layouts-example.jpg 1989w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:50px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-180{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-180{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-180 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-left:0px;" id="wordpresspages"><h2 class="title-heading-left" style="margin:0;">Explaining WordPress Pages vs. Posts</h2></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-143"><p>Website pages are allocated for static content such as your website&#8217;s homepage, about, contact page, and so on, and are timeless entities.</p>
<p>Website posts are allocated to blog content listed in reverse (newest to the oldest) chronological order and are timely. Older posts are archived based on month and year. You can also create content for custom post types or CPT. In Avada, an example of this is the Portfolio post type. Check out this detailed <a href="https://wordpress.com/support/post-vs-page/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WordPress article</a> for more information.</p>
</div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:50px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-181{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-181{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-181 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-left:0px;" id="change"><h2 class="title-heading-left" style="margin:0;">What Can I Change? Is the Design Flexible?</h2></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-144"><p>The <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/avada-builder/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Avada Builder</a> prebuilt website is exactly that, prebuilt, for you. If the design and style suit your website needs, you can use it as a starting point, and you can change as much or as little as you need to.</p>
<p>The most obvious details that you will want to change at first is the website&#8217;s wording, titles, color scheme, and images. You can choose to leave the overall layouts as is or Drag and Drop to rearrange the content&#8217;s order. Further to that, you can add or remove any of the <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Design </a><a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Elements </a>to fine-tune your preferred business narrative. In short, you can change every single aspect of the prebuilt website&#8217;s Layout and content.</p>
<p>Editing a page&#8217;s content and layouts is done using the <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/avada-live/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Drag and Drop</a> live editor or using the traditional back-end method. The first image below shows the Live visual Drag and Drop editor is used to edit the content:</p>
</div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-69 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-live-Editing.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[c7481e5b6222807c5db]" data-title="Avada Builder live Editing" title="Avada Builder live Editing"><img width="1920" height="936" alt="Live Editor" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-live-Editing.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-854932" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-live-Editing-200x98.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-live-Editing-400x195.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-live-Editing-600x293.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-live-Editing-800x390.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-live-Editing-1200x585.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-live-Editing.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-145"><p>The image below shows the traditional back-end method is used to edit the content:</p>
</div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-70 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Backend-Editing.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[5ee60403404194c3ff5]" data-title="Avada Builder Backend Editing" title="Avada Builder Backend Editing"><img width="1905" height="864" alt="Back-end Editing" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Backend-Editing.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-854896" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Backend-Editing-200x91.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Backend-Editing-400x181.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Backend-Editing-600x272.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Backend-Editing-800x363.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Backend-Editing-1200x544.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Backend-Editing.jpg 1905w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:50px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-182{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-182{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-182 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-left:0px;" id="comparison"><h2 class="title-heading-left" style="margin:0;">A Side By Side Comparison</h2></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-146"><p>We have created a side by side point of reference that illustrates the differences in building a website using the Avada Website Builder to design custom Layouts vs. not using The Avada Website Builder and only using predefined options. The latter will allow you only to build a basic site, in comparison.</p>
</div><ul class="fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-33" style="font-size:16px;line-height:27.2px;"><li class="fusion-li-item"><span style="height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;" class="icon-wrapper circle-no"><i class="fusion-li-icon fa-check fas" style="color:#4e6d43;" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><div class="fusion-li-item-content" style="margin-left:38.4px;"><a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/handmade/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Avada Handmade</a> (Using the Website Builder)</div></li><li class="fusion-li-item"><span style="height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;" class="icon-wrapper circle-no"><i class="fusion-li-icon fa-times fas" style="color:#4e6d43;" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><div class="fusion-li-item-content" style="margin-left:38.4px;"><a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/handmade-basic/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Avada Handmade Basic</a> (Not using the Website Builder)</div></li></ul><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:50px;width:100%;"></div></div><style type="text/css">.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-42{width:100% !important;margin-top : 20px;margin-bottom : 20px;}.fusion-builder-column-42 > .fusion-column-wrapper {padding-top : 0px !important;padding-right : 0px !important;margin-right : 1.92%;padding-bottom : 0px !important;padding-left : 0px !important;margin-left : 1.92%;}@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-42{width:100% !important;order : 0;}.fusion-builder-column-42 > .fusion-column-wrapper {margin-right : 1.92%;margin-left : 1.92%;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-42{width:100% !important;order : 0;}.fusion-builder-column-42 > .fusion-column-wrapper {margin-right : 1.92%;margin-left : 1.92%;}}</style></div></div><style type="text/css">.fusion-body .fusion-flex-container.fusion-builder-row-35{ padding-top : 0px;margin-top : 0px;padding-right : 0px;padding-bottom : 0px;margin-bottom : 0px;padding-left : 0px;}</style></div><div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-36 fusion-flex-container nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling" style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#eae9e9;border-style:solid;" ><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start" style="max-width:1352px;margin-left: calc(-4% / 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% / 2 );"><div class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-43 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column"><div class="fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column" style="background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;"><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-183{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-183{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-183 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-left:0px;" id="homepage"><h2 class="title-heading-left" style="margin:0;">Exploring The Homepage Layout</h2></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-184{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-184{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-184 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three" style="font-size:32px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h3 class="title-heading-left" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">The Header</h3></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-147"><p>For the <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/avada-builder/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Avada Builder</a> prebuilt website, the Header was created using the Avada <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/website-builder-features/avada-header-builder/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Header Builder</a> and is set globally across the website. This means that every page and post will use the same Header layout without any further conditions set. For example, you can change this if required by creating a unique Header layout for different pages or posts. You can check how this is structured on the backend by clicking this <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-header-backend.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">link</a>.</p>
</div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-71 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Header.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[922557b4e163a086b50]" data-title="Avada Builder Header" title="Avada Builder Header"><img width="1904" height="218" alt="AVada Virtual Assistant Header" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Header.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-854898" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Header-200x23.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Header-400x46.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Header-600x69.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Header-800x92.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Header-1200x137.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Header.jpg 1904w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:30px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-185{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-185{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-185 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three" style="font-size:32px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h3 class="title-heading-left" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">The Page Content</h3></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-148"><p>The content part of the homepage, the area between the Header and Footer, does not use a page title bar. You can change this page&#8217;s content in an infinite number of ways to best suit your business marketing and brand requirements.</p>
<p>Page and Post content is structured using Container and Column Elements, and if required, Nested Columns. Check out the help file links below for detailed information and videos explaining what they are and how to use them:</p>
</div><ul class="fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-34" style="font-size:16px;line-height:27.2px;"><li class="fusion-li-item"><span style="height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;" class="icon-wrapper circle-no"><i class="fusion-li-icon fa-info-circle fas" style="color:#4e6d43;" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><div class="fusion-li-item-content" style="margin-left:38.4px;">What are Containers, and how to use them? Read more <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/container-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a>.</div></li><li class="fusion-li-item"><span style="height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;" class="icon-wrapper circle-no"><i class="fusion-li-icon fa-info-circle fas" style="color:#4e6d43;" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><div class="fusion-li-item-content" style="margin-left:38.4px;">What are Columns, and how to use them? Read more <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/column-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a>.</div></li><li class="fusion-li-item"><span style="height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;" class="icon-wrapper circle-no"><i class="fusion-li-icon fa-info-circle fas" style="color:#4e6d43;" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><div class="fusion-li-item-content" style="margin-left:38.4px;">What are Nested Columns, and how to use them? Read more <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/nested-columns-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a>.</div></li></ul></div><style type="text/css">.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-43{width:100% !important;margin-top : 20px;margin-bottom : 20px;}.fusion-builder-column-43 > .fusion-column-wrapper {padding-top : 0px !important;padding-right : 0px !important;margin-right : 1.92%;padding-bottom : 0px !important;padding-left : 0px !important;margin-left : 1.92%;}@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-43{width:100% !important;order : 0;}.fusion-builder-column-43 > .fusion-column-wrapper {margin-right : 1.92%;margin-left : 1.92%;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-43{width:100% !important;order : 0;}.fusion-builder-column-43 > .fusion-column-wrapper {margin-right : 1.92%;margin-left : 1.92%;}}</style></div></div><style type="text/css">.fusion-body .fusion-flex-container.fusion-builder-row-36{ padding-top : 0px;margin-top : 0px;padding-right : 0px;padding-bottom : 0px;margin-bottom : 0px;padding-left : 0px;}</style></div><div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-37 fusion-flex-container nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling" style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#eae9e9;border-style:solid;" ><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start" style="max-width:1352px;margin-left: calc(-4% / 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% / 2 );"><div class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-44 fusion-flex-column"><div class="fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column" style="background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;"><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-186{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-186{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-186 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h4 class="title-heading-center" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">The Hero</h4></div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-72 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Hero.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[12e92f00ff36efa016d]" data-title="Avada Builder Hero" title="Avada Builder Hero"><img width="1903" height="425" alt="Avada Virtual Assistant Hero" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Hero.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-854934" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Hero-200x45.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Hero-400x89.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Hero-600x134.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Hero-800x179.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Hero-1200x268.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Hero.jpg 1903w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-149"><p>Instead of using a traditional image slider, like the <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/website-builder-features/avada-slider/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Avada Slider</a>, <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/website-builder-features/avada-third-party-integration/slider-revolution/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Slider Revolution</a> or <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/website-builder-features/avada-third-party-integration/layer-slider/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Layer Slider</a>, as the above-the-fold hero section, this prebuilt site uses a <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/container-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Container</a>. Added to the container are two (Left 65% and Right 35%) width <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/column-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Columns </a>with a <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/text-block-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Text Block Element</a> added to the left Column and <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/title-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Title</a>, <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/text-block-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Text</a>, and a <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/button-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Button Element</a> added to the right Column.</p>
</div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-187{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-187{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-187 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h4 class="title-heading-center" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">Visual CTAâ€™s</h4></div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-73 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-1.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[f2efc02b2cd6fb9e4d9]" data-title="Avada Builder CTA 1" title="Avada Builder CTA 1"><img width="1903" height="881" alt="Avada Virtual Assistant Info CTA" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-1.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-854939" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-1-200x93.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-1-400x185.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-1-600x278.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-1-800x370.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-1-1200x556.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-1.jpg 1903w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-150"><p>Using images as a way to highlight a call-to-action or for advertizing and promotion reasons is standard practice, and the <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/avada-website-builder/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Avada </a><a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/avada-website-builder/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Website </a><a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/avada-website-builder/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Builder</a> makes this task even easier for you. To create this section, a Container Element is added to the page content which has an image selected as the background overlay. To create the style, two (55% and 25.73% width) Columns are added to the Container. The column on the left contains a <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/title-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Title Element</a>, a <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/text-block-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Text Block Element</a>, and the <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/nested-columns-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Nested </a><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/nested-columns-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Columns Element</a> and the column on the right contains a <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/button-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Button Element</a>.</p>
<p>Padding and margin options are set for each Column to create that visual placement.</p>
</div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-188{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-188{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-188 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h4 class="title-heading-center" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">More Information &#8211; CTA</h4></div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-74 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-2.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[269449f9d1ce71b92b8]" data-title="Avada Builder CTA 2" title="Avada Builder CTA 2"><img width="1901" height="806" alt="Avada Virtual Assistant Info CTA" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-2.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-855021" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-2-200x85.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-2-400x170.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-2-600x254.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-2-800x339.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-2-1200x509.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-2.jpg 1901w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-151"><p>A Call-to-action (CTA) is a marketing method designed to prompt an immediate response or encourage a direct sale from your website visitors. There is no hard and fast rule about how you should create them, other than being an attraction and conversion point on your website. Using the Avada Design Elements, you can make any CTA style that you feel will work for your online business.</p>
<p>For this example, the CTA section is made up of two (1/2 â€“ 50%) Columns side by side. An <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/image-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Image Element</a> is added to the left Column. In the right Column you will see couple of <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/title-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Title Element&#8217;s</a>, a <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/text-block-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Text Block Element</a>, and a <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/button-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Button </a><a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/button-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Element</a>.</p>
</div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-189{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-189{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-189 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h4 class="title-heading-center" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">Available Properties</h4></div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-75 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builde-Available-Properties.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[955a9cf9bd253d395cc]" data-title="Avada Builde Available Properties" title="Avada Builde Available Properties"><img width="1904" height="866" alt="Avada Virtual Assistant Services" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builde-Available-Properties.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-855023" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builde-Available-Properties-200x91.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builde-Available-Properties-400x182.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builde-Available-Properties-600x273.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builde-Available-Properties-800x364.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builde-Available-Properties-1200x546.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builde-Available-Properties.jpg 1904w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-152"><p>This section pretty straightforward and easy to replicate. It starts with a <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/container-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Container</a>. Two (1/2 &#8211; 50%) width <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/column-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Columns</a> is added to the container, of which the left column displays a <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/title-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Title Element</a> and a <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/button-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Button Element</a> in the right Column.</p>
<p>Below the two (1/2 50%) width Columns is a single row of 3 (1/ &#8211; 33.33%) Columns, each containing a <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/nested-columns-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Nested Columns Element</a>. For this example, each of these Nested columns, which are columns containing columns, a 100% width Column, which holds a Title Element, <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/text-block-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Text Block Element</a> is added. Following this, two (1/2 50%) width columns are added, each containing two <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/text-block-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Text Blocks</a> and a Title Element.</p>
<p>Lastly, we have two more 100% width Columns, of which one contains <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/text-block-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Text</a> and Title Elements and the last an <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/image-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Image Element</a>.</p>
</div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-190{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-190{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-190 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h4 class="title-heading-center" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">CTA &#8211; Call to Action</h4></div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-76 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-banner.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[96f1334398e4707d3dd]" data-title="Avada Builder banner" title="Avada Builder banner"><img width="1903" height="676" alt="Avada Virtual Assistant Main CTA" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-banner.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-855030" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-banner-200x71.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-banner-400x142.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-banner-600x213.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-banner-800x284.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-banner-1200x426.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-banner.jpg 1903w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-153"><p>A standard Call-to-action (CTA) is illustrated below and is set up in a single container with an image background. Inside the container you will find a (1/1 &#8211; 100%) <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/column-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Column</a> with a <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/button-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Button Element</a>.</p>
<p>Depending on the marketing goal, CTA&#8217;s can drive a variety of different actions and results for your website visitors. Check this article for some CTA inspiration, <a href="https://blog.hubspot.com/marketing/call-to-action-examples" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">39 Call-to-Action Examples You Can&#8217;t Help But Click</a>.</p>
</div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-191{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-191{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-191 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h4 class="title-heading-center" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">Guided Tour</h4></div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-77 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Guided-tour.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[2ddcf6e6d4cce7e0a11]" data-title="Avada Builder Guided tour" title="Avada Builder Guided tour"><img width="1904" height="780" alt="Avada Virtual Assistant Nested Columns" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Guided-tour.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-855031" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Guided-tour-200x82.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Guided-tour-400x164.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Guided-tour-600x246.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Guided-tour-800x328.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Guided-tour-1200x492.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Guided-tour.jpg 1904w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-154"><p>This section a 1/1 (100% width) Column with a <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/title-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Title Element</a> and located below this 1/3 (33.33% width) Columns and uses the versatile <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/nested-columns-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Nested Column Element</a>, and simply put are Columns within Columns. For this example, you can add a 100% width Column in each of three 1/3 (33.33% width) Columns. This will mean that the Nested Column will be 1/1 (100%) width of each of the 1/3 Column. Each of these 1/1 (100% width) Columns, contains a background image.</p>
<p>Located in the 1/3 (33.33% width), below the above mentioned Nested Columns, is another Nested Column. These Nested Columns each contain a <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/text-block-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Text Block Element</a>, Title Element and a Button Element. The <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/button-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Button Element</a> in this example uses Anchor scrolling. Anchor Scrolling can be used to link to a different section on the same page, or a specific section on a different page. Read this <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/how-to/how-to-use-anchor-scrolling/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">help file</a> for more information.</p>
</div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-192{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-192{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-192 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h4 class="title-heading-center" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">More Information &#8211; CTA</h4></div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-78 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-3.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[7174177984304825b64]" data-title="Avada Builder CTA 3" title="Avada Builder CTA 3"><img width="1903" height="422" alt="Avada Virtual Assistant Brands" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-3.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-855056" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-3-200x44.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-3-400x89.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-3-600x133.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-3-800x177.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-3-1200x266.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-3.jpg 1903w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-155"><p>A Call-to-action (CTA) is a marketing method designed to prompt an immediate response or encourage a direct sale from your website visitors. There is no hard and fast rule about how you should create them, other than being an attraction and conversion point on your website. Using the Avada Design Elements, you can make any CTA style that you feel will work for your online business.</p>
<p>For this example, the CTA section is made up of two (Left 35% and Right 65% width) Columns side by side. A Tile and <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/text-block-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Text Box Element</a> is added to the left Column. In the right Column you will see a couple of <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/title-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Title Element&#8217;s</a>.</p>
</div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-193{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-193{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-193 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h4 class="title-heading-center" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">Visual CTAâ€™s</h4></div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-79 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-4.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[1c77472afb18cf42ea9]" data-title="Avada Builder CTA 4" title="Avada Builder CTA 4"><img width="1904" height="679" alt="Avada Virtual Assistant Nested Columns" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-4.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-855061" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-4-200x71.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-4-400x143.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-4-600x214.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-4-800x285.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-4-1200x428.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-4.jpg 1904w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-156"><p>Here is another section using visual CTA&#8217;s. Using images as a way to highlight a call-to-action or for advertizing and promotion reasons is standard practice, and the <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/avada-website-builder/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Avada Website Builder</a> makes this task even easier for you. To create this section, a Container Element is added to the page content which has an image selected as the background overlay.</p>
<p>Inside the container you will find a 1/1 (100% width) Column containing a couple of <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/title-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Title Elements</a> and a <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/button-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Button Element</a>.</p>
</div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-194{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-194{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-194 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h4 class="title-heading-center" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">Latest Articles</h4></div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-80 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-latest-articles.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[857db4a97a6d49f18ba]" data-title="Avada Builder latest articles" title="Avada Builder latest articles"><img width="1902" height="876" alt="Avada Virtual Assistant Nested Columns" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-latest-articles.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-855300" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-latest-articles-200x92.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-latest-articles-400x184.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-latest-articles-600x276.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-latest-articles-800x368.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-latest-articles-1200x553.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-latest-articles.jpg 1902w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-157"><p>This section is similar to the &#8220;Available Properties&#8221; section. It starts with a Container. Two (1/2 &#8211; 50%) width Columns is added to the container, of which the left column displays a Title Element and a Button Element in the right Column.</p>
<p><span style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); letter-spacing: 0px; font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal);">Below the two (1/2 50%) width Columns is a single row of 3 (1/ &#8211; 33.33%) Columns, each containing a Nested Columns Element. For this example, each of these Nested columns, which are columns containing columns, have two 100% width Columns below each other, of which the first holds an <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/image-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Image Element</a> and the second a <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/title-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Title Element</a>, <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/text-block-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Text Block Element</a> and a <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/button-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Button Element</a></span><span style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); letter-spacing: 0px; font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal);">.</span></p>
</div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-195{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-195{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-195 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h4 class="title-heading-center" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">Subscription Form</h4></div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-81 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-subscription-form.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[a03d0b3d3f68be4d6b9]" data-title="Avada Builder subscription form" title="Avada Builder subscription form"><img width="1903" height="877" alt="Avada Virtual Assistant Nested Columns" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-subscription-form.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-855303" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-subscription-form-200x92.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-subscription-form-400x184.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-subscription-form-600x277.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-subscription-form-800x369.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-subscription-form-1200x553.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-subscription-form.jpg 1903w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-158"><p>The <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/website-builder-features/avada-form-builder/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Avada Form Builder</a> is used to design and build this subscription form. The Form Builder is very flexible and allows you to create many types of forms that you can use on your <a href="https://bit.ly/2NccgzM" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Avada </a>website. For any form that you create, you can add them to a page or post as a single instance or you can set the form to display <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/forms/avada-forms-global-options/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">globally</a> across the website, which then allows you to manage one form. If a form is showing on all pages, for example, and you edit the form, the same changes show across all form instances.</p>
</div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-196{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-196{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-196 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h4 class="title-heading-center" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">More Information &#8211; CTA</h4></div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-82 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-informatation.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[e63c8c142bbc5c679d4]" data-title="Avada Builder informatation" title="Avada Builder informatation"><img width="1897" height="892" alt="Avada Virtual Assistant Nested Columns" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-informatation.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-855304" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-informatation-200x94.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-informatation-400x188.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-informatation-600x282.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-informatation-800x376.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-informatation-1200x564.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-informatation.jpg 1897w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-159"><p>A Call-to-action (CTA) is a marketing method designed to prompt an immediate response or encourage a direct sale from your website visitors. There is no hard and fast rule about how you should create them, other than being an attraction and conversion point on your website. Using the Avada Design Elements, you can make any CTA style that you feel will work for your online business.</p>
<p>For this example, the CTA section is made up of two (1/2 â€“ 50%) Columns side by side. An <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/image-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Image Element</a> is added to the right Column. In the left Column you will see couple of <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/title-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Title Element&#8217;s</a>, a <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/text-block-element/">Text Block Element</a>, and a <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/button-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Button Element</a>.</p>
</div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-197{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-197{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-197 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h4 class="title-heading-center" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">Visual CTA&#8217;s</h4></div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-83 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-5.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[ab701b26f1ddcfc07aa]" data-title="Avada Builder CTA 5" title="Avada Builder CTA 5"><img width="1903" height="884" alt="Avada Virtual Assistant Nested Columns" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-5.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-855305" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-5-200x93.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-5-400x186.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-5-600x279.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-5-800x372.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-5-1200x557.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-CTA-5.jpg 1903w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-160"><p>Following using another visual CTA&#8217;s. As said before, using images as a way to highlight a call-to-action or for advertizing and promotion reasons is standard practice, and the <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/avada-website-builder/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Avada Website Builder</a> makes this task even easier for you. To create this section, a Container Element is added to the page content which has an image selected as the background overlay.</p>
<p>Inside the container you will find a two (50% left and 25.73% right width) Columns containing a couple of <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/text-block-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Text Block Elements</a> and <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/title-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Title Element</a> on the left and a <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/button-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Button Element</a> in the right Column.</p>
</div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-198{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-198{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-198 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h4 class="title-heading-center" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">Our Clients</h4></div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-84 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Our-clients.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[f264822ae73f9dcdd91]" data-title="Avada Builder Our clients" title="Avada Builder Our clients"><img width="1898" height="608" alt="Avada Virtual Assistant Nested Columns" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Our-clients.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-855310" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Our-clients-200x64.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Our-clients-400x128.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Our-clients-600x192.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Our-clients-800x256.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Our-clients-1200x384.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Avada-Builder-Our-clients.jpg 1898w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-161"><p>This section does well to highlight client partnerships or repurposed to showcase information related to your services and products, and more. Right now, the setup is single full width (1/1 â€“ 100%) Column with a <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/title-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Title Element</a>. Below are two rows of 3 (1/3 â€“ 33.33%) Columns, each with an <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/image-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Image Element</a>.</p>
<p>As an alternative, an <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/image-carousel-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Image Carousel Element</a> can be used for a similar visual effect.</p>
</div></div><style type="text/css">.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-44{width:100% !important;margin-top : 20px;margin-bottom : 20px;}.fusion-builder-column-44 > .fusion-column-wrapper {padding-top : 0px !important;padding-right : 0px !important;margin-right : 1.92%;padding-bottom : 0px !important;padding-left : 0px !important;margin-left : 1.92%;}@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-44{width:100% !important;order : 0;}.fusion-builder-column-44 > .fusion-column-wrapper {margin-right : 1.92%;margin-left : 1.92%;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-44{width:100% !important;order : 0;}.fusion-builder-column-44 > .fusion-column-wrapper {margin-right : 1.92%;margin-left : 1.92%;}}</style></div></div><style type="text/css">.fusion-body .fusion-flex-container.fusion-builder-row-37{ padding-top : 0px;margin-top : 0px;padding-right : 0px;padding-bottom : 0px;margin-bottom : 0px;padding-left : 0px;}</style></div><div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-38 fusion-flex-container nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling" style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#eae9e9;border-style:solid;" ><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start" style="max-width:1352px;margin-left: calc(-4% / 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% / 2 );"><div class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-45 fusion-flex-column"><div class="fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column" style="background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;"><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-199{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-199{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-199 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;" id="footer"><h2 class="title-heading-left" style="margin:0;">The Footer</h2></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-162"><p>A website footer aims to help visitors by providing appropriate information and navigation options at the bottom of website pages. Website footer design is underrated and more valuable to your website than you may think and is essential to the overall end-user experience. Three key points stand out, namely:</p>
</div><ul class="fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-35" style="font-size:16px;line-height:27.2px;"><li class="fusion-li-item"><span style="height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;" class="icon-wrapper circle-no"><i class="fusion-li-icon fa-thumbs-up fas" style="color:#4e6d43;" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><div class="fusion-li-item-content" style="margin-left:38.4px;">A footer should provide a website visitor with additional choices. If you want people to sign up for your mailing list, view a product demo, or contact you, inviting them at the end of a scroll is a compelling call to action.</div></li><li class="fusion-li-item"><span style="height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;" class="icon-wrapper circle-no"><i class="fusion-li-icon fa-thumbs-up fas" style="color:#4e6d43;" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><div class="fusion-li-item-content" style="margin-left:38.4px;">A footer should create a path for continued engagement by including navigation links to products, services, or other parts of your website.</div></li><li class="fusion-li-item"><span style="height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;" class="icon-wrapper circle-no"><i class="fusion-li-icon fa-thumbs-up fas" style="color:#4e6d43;" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><div class="fusion-li-item-content" style="margin-left:38.4px;">A footer can access essential information like ways to contact your company and customer services, privacy statements, and potential legal disclaimers.</div></li></ul><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-163"><p>For the <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/avada-builder/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Avada Builder</a> prebuilt website, the Footer was created using the Avada <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/website-builder-features/avada-footer-builder/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Footer Builder</a> and this particular Footer content and Layout is set to display globally across the website. This means that every page and post will use the same Footer layout without any further conditions set. For example, you can change this if required by creating a unique Footer layout for different pages or posts. Let us take a closer look below:</p>
</div></div><style type="text/css">.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-45{width:100% !important;margin-top : 20px;margin-bottom : 20px;}.fusion-builder-column-45 > .fusion-column-wrapper {padding-top : 0px !important;padding-right : 0px !important;margin-right : 1.92%;padding-bottom : 0px !important;padding-left : 0px !important;margin-left : 1.92%;}@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-45{width:100% !important;order : 0;}.fusion-builder-column-45 > .fusion-column-wrapper {margin-right : 1.92%;margin-left : 1.92%;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-45{width:100% !important;order : 0;}.fusion-builder-column-45 > .fusion-column-wrapper {margin-right : 1.92%;margin-left : 1.92%;}}</style></div><div class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-46 fusion-flex-column"><div class="fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column" style="background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;"><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-200{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-200{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-200 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h4 class="title-heading-center" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">Footer Content</h4></div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-85 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e