ling" style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#eae9e9;border-style:solid;" ><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start" style="max-width:1352px;margin-left: calc(-4% / 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% / 2 );"><div class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-58 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column"><div class="fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column" style="background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;"><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-259{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-259{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-259 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-left:0px;" id="layouts"><h2 class="title-heading-left" style="margin:0;">Explaining Layouts &amp; Layout Sections</h2></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-205"><p>Before we look at the specific Layouts on the Avada Handmade prebuilt website, the first thing to understand is the Layouts and Layout Sections&#8217; architecture. You can think of Layouts as a container for the page content. In contrast, the actual content comes from the various Layout Sections. There are four Layout Sections on a page â€“ the Header, Page Title Bar, Content, and Footer Layout Sections.</p>
<p>There is a default Global Layout, and any Layout Sections added to that will be shown on all pages of your website. There are Conditional Layouts with conditional logic to determine how the Layout will be used.</p>
<p>You can make as many Layouts and Layout Sections as you like, and you can use the Layout Sections in multiple Layouts. But you can only use a specific condition on a single Layout, so the theme knows which one to use.</p>
<p>See <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/fusion-builder/theme-builder/understanding-layouts-and-layout-sections/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Understanding Layouts &amp; Layout Sections</a> and <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/fusion-builder/theme-builder/understanding-conditional-layouts/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Understanding Conditional Layouts</a> for more info.</p>
</div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-101 hover-type-none"><img width="1989" height="1500" alt="Avada Layouts" title="Avada Layouts" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avadawebsitebuilder-layouts-example.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-840348" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avadawebsitebuilder-layouts-example-200x151.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avadawebsitebuilder-layouts-example-400x302.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avadawebsitebuilder-layouts-example-600x452.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avadawebsitebuilder-layouts-example-800x603.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avadawebsitebuilder-layouts-example-1200x905.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avadawebsitebuilder-layouts-example.jpg 1989w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:50px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-260{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-260{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-260 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-left:0px;" id="wordpresspages"><h2 class="title-heading-left" style="margin:0;">Explaining WordPress Pages vs. Posts</h2></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-206"><p>Website pages are allocated for static content such as your website&#8217;s homepage, about, contact page, and so on, and are timeless entities.</p>
<p>Website posts are allocated to blog content listed in reverse (newest to the oldest) chronological order and are timely. Older posts are archived based on month and year. You can also create content for custom post types or CPT. In Avada, an example of this is the Portfolio post type. Check out this detailed <a href="https://wordpress.com/support/post-vs-page/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WordPress article</a> for more information.</p>
</div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:50px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-261{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-261{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-261 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-left:0px;" id="change"><h2 class="title-heading-left" style="margin:0;">What Can I Change? Is the Design Flexible?</h2></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-207"><p>The <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/handmade/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Avada Handmade</a> prebuilt website is exactly that, prebuilt, for you. If the design and style suit your website needs, you can use it as a starting point, and you can change as much or as little as you need to.</p>
<p>The most obvious details that you will want to change at first is the website&#8217;s wording, titles, color scheme, and images. You can choose to leave the overall layouts as is or Drag and Drop to rearrange the content&#8217;s order. Further to that, you can add or remove any of the <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Design Elements</a> to fine-tune your preferred business narrative. In short, you can change every single aspect of the prebuilt website&#8217;s Layout and content.</p>
<p>Editing a page&#8217;s content and layouts is done using the <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/avada-live/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Drag and Drop</a> live editor or using the traditional back-end method. The first image below shows the Live visual Drag and Drop editor is used to edit the content:</p>
</div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-102 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-hero-live-edit.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[27dc71189e4876f387d]" data-title="Live Editor" title="Live Editor"><img width="1900" height="937" alt="Live Editor" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-hero-live-edit.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-848649" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-hero-live-edit-200x99.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-hero-live-edit-400x197.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-hero-live-edit-600x296.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-hero-live-edit-800x395.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-hero-live-edit-1200x592.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-hero-live-edit.jpg 1900w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-208"><p>The image below shows the traditional back-end method is used to edit the content:</p>
</div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-103 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-backend-editing.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[734a22e3a445f09a36e]" data-title="Back-end Editing" title="Back-end Editing"><img width="1900" height="919" alt="Back-end Editing" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-backend-editing.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-848653" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-backend-editing-200x97.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-backend-editing-400x193.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-backend-editing-600x290.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-backend-editing-800x387.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-backend-editing-1200x580.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-backend-editing.jpg 1900w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:50px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-262{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-262{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-262 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-left:0px;" id="comparison"><h2 class="title-heading-left" style="margin:0;">A Side By Side Comparison</h2></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-209"><p>We have created a side by side point of reference that illustrates the differences in building a website using the Avada Website Builder to design custom Layouts vs. not using The Avada Website Builder and only using predefined options. The latter will allow you only to build a basic site, in comparison.</p>
</div><ul class="fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-46" style="font-size:16px;line-height:27.2px;"><li class="fusion-li-item"><span style="height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;" class="icon-wrapper circle-no"><i class="fusion-li-icon fa-check fas" style="color:#bc4b20;" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><div class="fusion-li-item-content" style="margin-left:38.4px;"><a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/handmade/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Avada Handmade</a> (Using the Website Builder)</div></li><li class="fusion-li-item"><span style="height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;" class="icon-wrapper circle-no"><i class="fusion-li-icon fa-times fas" style="color:#bc4b20;" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><div class="fusion-li-item-content" style="margin-left:38.4px;"><a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/handmade-basic/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Avada Handmade Basic</a> (Not using the Website Builder)</div></li></ul><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:50px;width:100%;"></div></div><style type="text/css">.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-58{width:100% !important;margin-top : 20px;margin-bottom : 20px;}.fusion-builder-column-58 > .fusion-column-wrapper {padding-top : 0px !important;padding-right : 0px !important;margin-right : 1.92%;padding-bottom : 0px !important;padding-left : 0px !important;margin-left : 1.92%;}@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-58{width:100% !important;order : 0;}.fusion-builder-column-58 > .fusion-column-wrapper {margin-right : 1.92%;margin-left : 1.92%;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-58{width:100% !important;order : 0;}.fusion-builder-column-58 > .fusion-column-wrapper {margin-right : 1.92%;margin-left : 1.92%;}}</style></div></div><style type="text/css">.fusion-body .fusion-flex-container.fusion-builder-row-47{ padding-top : 0px;margin-top : 0px;padding-right : 0px;padding-bottom : 0px;margin-bottom : 0px;padding-left : 0px;}</style></div><div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-48 fusion-flex-container nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling" style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#eae9e9;border-style:solid;" ><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start" style="max-width:1352px;margin-left: calc(-4% / 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% / 2 );"><div class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-59 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column"><div class="fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column" style="background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;"><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-263{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-263{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-263 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-left:0px;" id="homepage"><h2 class="title-heading-left" style="margin:0;">Exploring The Homepage Layout</h2></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-264{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-264{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-264 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three" style="font-size:32px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h3 class="title-heading-left" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">The Header</h3></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-210"><p>For the <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/handmade/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Avada Handmade</a> prebuilt website, the Header was created using the Avada <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/website-builder-features/avada-header-builder/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Header Builder</a> and is set globally across the website. This means that every page and post will use the same Header layout without any further conditions set. For example, you can change this if required by creating a unique Header layout for different pages or posts. You can check how this is structured on the backend by clicking this <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/handmade-header-backend.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-rel="iLightbox">link</a>.</p>
</div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-104 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-header-slice.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[af4188914c5ea08038c]" data-title="Handmade header" title="Handmade header"><img width="1900" height="172" alt="Handmade Header" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-header-slice.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-840629" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-header-slice-200x18.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-header-slice-400x36.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-header-slice-600x54.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-header-slice-800x72.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-header-slice-1200x109.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-header-slice.jpg 1900w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:30px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-265{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-265{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-265 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three" style="font-size:32px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h3 class="title-heading-left" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">The Page Content</h3></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-211"><p>The content part of the homepage, the area between the Header and Footer, does not use a page title bar. You can change this page&#8217;s content in an infinite number of ways to best suit your business marketing and brand requirements.</p>
<p>Page and Post content is structured using Container and Column Elements, and if required, Nested Columns. Check out the help file links below for detailed information and videos explaining what they are and how to use them:</p>
</div><ul class="fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-47" style="font-size:16px;line-height:27.2px;"><li class="fusion-li-item"><span style="height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;" class="icon-wrapper circle-no"><i class="fusion-li-icon fa-info-circle fas" style="color:#bc4b20;" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><div class="fusion-li-item-content" style="margin-left:38.4px;">What are Containers, and how to use them? Read more <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/container-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a>.</div></li><li class="fusion-li-item"><span style="height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;" class="icon-wrapper circle-no"><i class="fusion-li-icon fa-info-circle fas" style="color:#bc4b20;" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><div class="fusion-li-item-content" style="margin-left:38.4px;">What are Columns, and how to use them? Read more <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/column-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a>.</div></li><li class="fusion-li-item"><span style="height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;" class="icon-wrapper circle-no"><i class="fusion-li-icon fa-info-circle fas" style="color:#bc4b20;" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><div class="fusion-li-item-content" style="margin-left:38.4px;">What are Nested Columns, and how to use them? Read more <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/nested-columns-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a>.</div></li></ul></div><style type="text/css">.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-59{width:100% !important;margin-top : 20px;margin-bottom : 20px;}.fusion-builder-column-59 > .fusion-column-wrapper {padding-top : 0px !important;padding-right : 0px !important;margin-right : 1.92%;padding-bottom : 0px !important;padding-left : 0px !important;margin-left : 1.92%;}@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-59{width:100% !important;order : 0;}.fusion-builder-column-59 > .fusion-column-wrapper {margin-right : 1.92%;margin-left : 1.92%;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-59{width:100% !important;order : 0;}.fusion-builder-column-59 > .fusion-column-wrapper {margin-right : 1.92%;margin-left : 1.92%;}}</style></div></div><style type="text/css">.fusion-body .fusion-flex-container.fusion-builder-row-48{ padding-top : 0px;margin-top : 0px;padding-right : 0px;padding-bottom : 0px;margin-bottom : 0px;padding-left : 0px;}</style></div><div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-49 fusion-flex-container nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling" style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#eae9e9;border-style:solid;" ><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start" style="max-width:1352px;margin-left: calc(-4% / 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% / 2 );"><div class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-60 fusion-flex-column"><div class="fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column" style="background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;"><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-266{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-266{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-266 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h4 class="title-heading-center" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">The Hero</h4></div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-105 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-hero-slice.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[7017c3da32d92254b05]" data-title="Handmade Hero Section" title="Handmade Hero Section"><img width="1900" height="576" alt="Handmade Hero Section" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-hero-slice.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-840637" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-hero-slice-200x61.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-hero-slice-400x121.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-hero-slice-600x182.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-hero-slice-800x243.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-hero-slice-1200x364.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-hero-slice.jpg 1900w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-212"><p>Instead of using a traditional image slider, like the <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/website-builder-features/avada-slider/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Avada Slider</a> or <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/website-builder-features/avada-third-party-integration/slider-revolution/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Slider Revolution</a>, as the above-the-fold hero section, this prebuilt site uses a <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/container-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Container</a>. Added to that are three (1/3 &#8211; 33%) width <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/column-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Columns</a> and a <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/nested-columns-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Nested Column</a> within each Column.</p>
</div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-267{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-267{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-267 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h4 class="title-heading-center" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">Content Boxes</h4></div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-106 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-boxes-slice.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[48af49297d213550329]" data-title="Content Boxes" title="Content Boxes"><img width="1900" height="202" alt="Content Boxes" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-boxes-slice.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-840647" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-boxes-slice-200x21.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-boxes-slice-400x43.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-boxes-slice-600x64.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-boxes-slice-800x85.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-boxes-slice-1200x128.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-boxes-slice.jpg 1900w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-213"><p>The <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/content-boxes-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Content Box Element</a> is a handy and flexible Element with a wide range of styling options that you can use in so many different ways. In this instance, they display value points for potential product buyers and can be changed to best your website&#8217;s messaging.</p>
</div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-268{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-268{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-268 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h4 class="title-heading-center" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">CTA &#8211; Call to Action</h4></div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-107 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-cta-slice.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[9762437275d0cc0cffa]" data-title="Call to Action" title="Call to Action"><img width="1900" height="267" alt="Call to Action" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-cta-slice.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-840652" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-cta-slice-200x28.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-cta-slice-400x56.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-cta-slice-600x84.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-cta-slice-800x112.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-cta-slice-1200x169.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-cta-slice.jpg 1900w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-214"><p>A Call-to-action (CTA) is a marketing method designed to prompt an immediate response or encourage a direct sale from your website visitors. There is no hard and fast rule about how you should create them, other than being an attraction and conversion point on your website. Using the Avada Design Elements, you can make any CTA style that you feel will work for your online business.</p>
<p>For this example, the CTA section is made up of a <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/title-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Title Element</a>, a <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/text-block-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Text Block Element</a>, and a <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/button-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Button Element</a>.</p>
</div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-269{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-269{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-269 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h4 class="title-heading-center" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">Popular Categories</h4></div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-108 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-popularcats-slice.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[4d986982cd842dea34d]" data-title="Popular Categories" title="Popular Categories"><img width="1900" height="433" alt="Popular Categories" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-popularcats-slice.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-840663" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-popularcats-slice-200x46.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-popularcats-slice-400x91.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-popularcats-slice-600x137.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-popularcats-slice-800x182.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-popularcats-slice-1200x273.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-popularcats-slice.jpg 1900w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-215"><p>There are various ways to display popular product categories, using WooCommerce or, as in this instance, a series of four columns is used to direct the website visitor. Assigned to each <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/column-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Column Element</a> is an <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/image-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Image Element</a> and then below that, a <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/title-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Title Element</a>.</p>
<p>The final point to highlight is that each of the four columns is a clickable area by enabling the <strong>Link URL</strong> option within the Column Element settings.</p>
</div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-270{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-270{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-270 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;" id="subscriptionform"><h4 class="title-heading-center" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">Subscription Form</h4></div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-109 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-subscribe-slice.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[9d4e2e9e1143b9f777b]" data-title="Subscription Form" title="Subscription Form"><img width="1900" height="230" alt="Subscription Form" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-subscribe-slice.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-840668" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-subscribe-slice-200x24.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-subscribe-slice-400x48.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-subscribe-slice-600x73.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-subscribe-slice-800x97.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-subscribe-slice-1200x145.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-subscribe-slice.jpg 1900w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-216"><p>The <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/website-builder-features/avada-form-builder/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Avada Form Builder</a> is used to design and build this subscription form. The Form Builder is very flexible and allows you to create many types of forms that you can use on your <a href="https://bit.ly/2NhBSeq" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Avada</a> website. For any form that you create, you can add them to a page or post as a single instance or you can set the form to display <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/forms/avada-forms-global-options/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">globally</a> across the website, which then allows you to manage one form. If a form is showing on all pages, for example, and you edit the form, the same changes show across all form instances.</p>
</div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-271{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-271{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-271 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h4 class="title-heading-center" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">Editor&#8217;s Pick</h4></div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-110 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/editors-pick-section.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[6b27f1ff8dd4fb71ef3]" data-title="Editor&#8217;s Pick" title="Editor&#8217;s Pick"><img width="1900" height="936" alt="Editor&#039;s Pick" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/editors-pick-section.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-850288" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/editors-pick-section-200x99.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/editors-pick-section-400x197.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/editors-pick-section-600x296.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/editors-pick-section-800x394.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/editors-pick-section-1200x591.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/editors-pick-section.jpg 1900w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /><