</div>[recent_products limit="10" columns="5" orderby="rand" order="desc"]<div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:50px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-272{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-272{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-272 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h4 class="title-heading-center" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">Product CTA&#8217;s</h4></div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-111 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/product-ctas.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[1e6e894c98c5e644e0b]" data-title="Product CTA&#8217;s" title="Product CTA&#8217;s"><img width="1900" height="934" alt="Product CTA&#039;s" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/product-ctas.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-850292" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/product-ctas-200x98.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/product-ctas-400x197.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/product-ctas-600x295.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/product-ctas-800x393.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/product-ctas-1200x590.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/product-ctas.jpg 1900w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-218"><p>As shown in the image above, two Containers are added to the page content to advertize segmented product lines. The first <a href="https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/container-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Container Element</a> has a 2/3 Column and a 1/1 Column below that. The 2/3 Column houses two <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/title-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Title Elements</a>, a <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/text-block-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Text Block Element</a> for come text, and a <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/button-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Button Element</a>. The 1/1 Column has a <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/section-separator-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Section Separator Element</a> using the paper style option for an enhanced visual effect.</p>
<p>The second Container Element has 6 Columns added, and to each, we have added an <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/image-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Image Element</a> and then below that, a <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/title-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Title Element</a>.</p>
<p>The final point to highlight is that each of the six columns is a clickable area by enabling the <strong>Link URL</strong> option within the Column Element settings.</p>
</div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:50px;width:100%;"></div><style type="text/css">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-273{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-273{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-273 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four" style="font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;"><h4 class="title-heading-center" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;">Holiday Decorations</h4></div><div ><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-112 hover-type-none" style="border:1px solid #e0dede;"><a href="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/holiday-decorations.jpg" class="fusion-lightbox" data-rel="iLightbox[f7ea8bc600b3ed82adb]" data-title="Holiday Decorations" title="Holiday Decorations"><img width="1900" height="786" alt="Holiday Decorations" src="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/holiday-decorations.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-850289" srcset="https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/holiday-decorations-200x83.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/holiday-decorations-400x165.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/holiday-decorations-600x248.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/holiday-decorations-800x331.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/holiday-decorations-1200x496.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/holiday-decorations.jpg 1900w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-219"><p>This section is also straight forward. It starts off with a <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/title-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Title Element</a>, a <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/text-block-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Text Block Element</a>, and then a <a href="https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/woo-shortcodes-element/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WooCommerce Shortcode Element</a> to display the products in one row of three. The parameters for the WooCommerce Shortcode Element are as follows:</p>
